title: Green
content:
Green may refer to:

  • Green armour
  • Adamant, a green-coloured metal.
  • Guthix, a god associated with the colour green.

NPCs[edit | edit source]

  • Tropical wagtail, a green bird.

Monsters[edit | edit source]

  • Dragons:
    • Baby green dragon
    • Green dragon
    • Brutal green dragon
  • Elvarg, a green dragon.
  • Green Guard
  • Swamp lizard, a green salamander.

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Event rewards:
    • Deflated green bouncy ball
    • Green bouncy ball
    • Green halloween mask
    • Green marionette
    • Green paper hat
    • Green partyhat
    • Green rainbow strand
  • Green dragonhide items:
    • Green dragonhide
    • Green dragon leather
    • Green d'hide body, and its trimmed and gold-trimmed versions.
    • Green d'hide chaps, and its trimmed and gold-trimmed versions.
    • Green d'hide vambraces
    • Green spiky vambraces
    • Green d'hide shield
  • Rometti's Fine Fashions items:
    • Green hat
    • Green robe top
    • Green robe bottoms
    • Green boots
  • The Eyes of Glouphrie items:
    • Green circle
    • Green pentagon
    • Green square
    • Green triangle
  • Treasure Trail items:
    • Bob's green shirt
    • Green boater
    • Green dragon mask
    • Green elegant blouse
    • Green elegant legs
    • Green elegant shirt
    • Green elegant skirt
    • Green firelighter
    • Green headband
  • Trouble Brewing rewards:
    • Green tricorn hat
    • Green naval shirt
    • Green navy slacks
  • Fremennik green cloak
  • Green cape
  • Green dark bow paint
  • Green dye
  • Green dye bellows, an item used in the Mourning's End Part I quest.
  • Green egg, an item used in the Barbarian Assault minigame.
  • Green gloop soup
  • Green logs
  • Green salamander
  • Green satchel
  • Green slayer helmet, and its imbued version.
  • Green toad, an item used in the Mourning's End Part I quest.
  • Short green guy, and its mixed and premade versions.

Other[edit | edit source]

  • The Green Gemstone, a dwarven mining company in Keldagrim and its associates:
    • Green Gemstone Gems
    • Green Gemstone Director
    • Green Gemstone Secretary
  • The Green Ghost, a location.
